<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Proposisi Makro & Mikro — Customer Journey Map</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #050505; color: #e5e5e5; overflow: hidden; }
        h1, h2, h3, h4, .serif { font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif; }
        .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
        ::selection { background: white; color: black; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0a0a0a; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #333; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #555; }

        .slide {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            transform: scale(0.97) translateY(20px);
        }
        .slide.active {
            opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto;
            transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
        }

        .slide-inner {
            width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; padding: 2rem 3rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .slide-inner { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
        }

        .grid-bg {
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                              linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 30%, transparent 75%);
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 30%, transparent 75%);
        }

        .glow-line {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,79,48,0.6), transparent);
        }

        .proposition-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .proposition-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border-color: rgba(255,79,48,0.2);
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.375rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: #a3a3a3;
        }
        .tag-orange { border-color: rgba(255,79,48,0.3); color: #FF4F30; }

        .number-circle {
            width: 32px; height: 32px; min-width: 32px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
            background: rgba(255,79,48,0.1); color: #FF4F30;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,79,48,0.2);
        }

        .macro-num {
            font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1;
            color: rgba(255,79,48,0.08); position: absolute; top: -0.5rem; left: 0.5rem;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 2px; z-index: 100;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #FF4F30, #c2410c);
            transition: width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .nav-btn {
            width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            color: #a3a3a3; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: white; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        .nav-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.2; cursor: not-allowed; }

        .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transition: all 0.3s; cursor: pointer; }
        .dot.active { background: #FF4F30; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,79,48,0.4); width: 24px; border-radius: 4px; }

        .fade-in-item {
            opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px);
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item {
            opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.5s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 0.6s; }
        .slide.active .fade-in-item:nth-child(7) { transition-delay: 0.7s; }

        .hero-glow {
            position: absolute; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,79,48,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .icon-box {
            width: 40px; height: 40px; min-width: 40px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }

        .slide-counter {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem; color: #525252;
        }

        .cpmk-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,79,48,0.06) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 50%, rgba(255,79,48,0.03) 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,79,48,0.15);
            border-radius: 20px; padding: 2.5rem;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .cpmk-card::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: -1px; left: 20%; right: 20%; height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,79,48,0.4), transparent);
        }

        .cpmk-badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(255,79,48,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,79,48,0.2);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #FF4F30; font-weight: 500;
        }

        .c3-badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(255,79,48,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,79,48,0.15);
            font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600;
            color: #FF4F30;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        }
        .float-anim { animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Progress Bar -->
<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar" style="width: 0%"></div>

<!-- Background Grid -->
<div class="grid-bg fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

<!-- Slide Container -->
<div class="relative w-full h-screen z-10" id="slideContainer">

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 0: COVER ============ -->
    <div class="slide active" data-slide="0">
        <div class="slide-inner text-center relative">
            <div class="hero-glow" style="top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%);"></div>

            <div class="fade-in-item mb-6">
                <span class="tag tag-orange">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF4F30]"></span>
                    Design Thinking
                </span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="fade-in-item text-5xl md:text-7xl font-medium leading-[0.9] tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
                Proposisi<br>
                <span class="text-[#FF4F30]">Makro</span> & <span class="text-[#FF4F30]">Mikro</span>
            </h1>

            <div class="fade-in-item glow-line w-48 mx-auto mb-6"></div>

            <p class="fade-in-item text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-400 font-light max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Customer Journey Map dan Analisis<br>Pengalaman Pengguna
            </p>

            <div class="fade-in-item flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">
                <span class="mono text-xs">Sub-CPMK 2</span>
                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-neutral-600"></span>
                <span class="mono text-xs">Pertemuan 5</span>
            </div>

            <div class="fade-in-item mt-12 text-neutral-600 text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-down" class="w-4 h-4 float-anim"></i>
                <span class="mono text-xs">Tekan → untuk mulai</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 1: SUB-CPMK 2 ============ -->
    <div class="slide" data-slide="1">
        <div class="slide-inner flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-full max-w-3xl">
                <div class="fade-in-item mb-8">
                    <span class="tag tag-orange">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF4F30]"></span>
                        Capaian Pembelajaran
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="fade-in-item cpmk-card">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6">
                        <div class="cpmk-badge flex-shrink-0">C3</div>
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <div class="cpmk-badge mb-4 w-fit">
                                <span>Sub-CPMK 2</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-200 font-light leading-relaxed">
                                Mahasiswa mampu <span class="text-white font-medium">mengumpulkan data pengguna</span> dan menyusunnya dalam bentuk <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">empathy map</span>, <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">user persona</span>, dan <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">customer journey</span>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-2"><i data-lucide="heart-handshake" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light">Empathy Map</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-2"><i data-lucide="user-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light">User Persona</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-2"><i data-lucide="route" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light">Customer Journey</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="fade-in-item mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-600 text-xs">
                    <i data-lucide="info" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                    <span class="mono">C3 — Mengaplikasikan</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 2: PROPOSISI MAKRO ============ -->
    <div class="slide" data-slide="2">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="fade-in-item mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="tag tag-orange">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF4F30]"></span>
                    Makro
                </span>
                <span class="slide-counter">03 / 09</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="fade-in-item text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-3">Proposisi Makro</h2>
            <p class="fade-in-item text-neutral-500 text-sm font-light mb-8">Struktur utama materi Customer Journey Map</p>
            <div class="fade-in-item glow-line w-32 mb-10"></div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="number-circle">1</div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed pt-1 text-[0.95rem]">
                        Customer Journey Map digunakan untuk <span class="text-white font-medium">memetakan pengalaman pengguna</span> dalam berinteraksi dengan produk atau layanan digital.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="number-circle">2</div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed pt-1 text-[0.95rem]">
                        Pengalaman pengguna terdiri atas <span class="text-white font-medium">tahapan aktivitas, touchpoint, emosi, kebutuhan,</span> dan <span class="text-white font-medium">pain point</span> pengguna.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="number-circle">3</div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed pt-1 text-[0.95rem]">
                        Customer Journey Map membantu <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">mengidentifikasi peluang perbaikan</span> pengalaman pengguna pada produk digital.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="number-circle">4</div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed pt-1 text-[0.95rem]">
                        Penyusunan Customer Journey Map dilakukan berdasarkan <span class="text-white font-medium">data hasil user research</span> dan <span class="text-white font-medium">user persona</span>.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="number-circle">5</div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed pt-1 text-[0.95rem]">
                        Customer Journey Map menjadi <span class="text-white font-medium">dasar pengembangan solusi digital</span> berbasis <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">human-centered design</span>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 3: MIKRO 1 ============ -->
    <div class="slide" data-slide="3">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="fade-in-item mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="tag">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/40"></span>
                    Mikro 1
                </span>
                <span class="slide-counter">04 / 09</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="fade-in-item text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Proposisi Mikro 1</h2>
            <p class="fade-in-item text-neutral-500 text-sm font-light mb-8">Memahami perjalanan pengguna secara visual</p>
            <div class="fade-in-item glow-line w-32 mb-10"></div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-4"><i data-lucide="route" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <p class="mono text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-2">1.1</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-[0.9rem]">
                        Customer Journey Map <span class="text-white font-medium">menggambarkan perjalanan pengguna</span> dari awal hingga akhir penggunaan layanan.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-4"><i data-lucide="eye" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <p class="mono text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-2">1.2</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-[0.9rem]">
                        Membantu <span class="text-white font-medium">memahami perilaku dan pengalaman</span> pengguna secara visual.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box mx-auto mb-4"><i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <p class="mono text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-2">1.3</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-[0.9rem]">
                        Digunakan dalam proses <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">Design Thinking</span> berbasis human-centered design.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 4: MIKRO 2 ============ -->
    <div class="slide" data-slide="4">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="fade-in-item mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="tag">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/40"></span>
                    Mikro 2
                </span>
                <span class="slide-counter">05 / 09</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="fade-in-item text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Proposisi Mikro 2</h2>
            <p class="fade-in-item text-neutral-500 text-sm font-light mb-8">Komponen utama pengalaman pengguna</p>
            <div class="fade-in-item glow-line w-32 mb-10"></div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-click" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <span class="mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mr-3">2.1</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-300 font-light text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-white font-medium">Aktivitas pengguna</span> menggambarkan tindakan pengguna pada setiap tahap perjalanan.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i data-lucide="touchpad" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <span class="mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mr-3">2.2</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-300 font-light text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-white font-medium">Touchpoint</span> menunjukkan titik interaksi antara pengguna dan sistem digital.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i data-lucide="heart-pulse" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <span class="mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mr-3">2.3</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-300 font-light text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-white font-medium">Emosi pengguna</span> menggambarkan perasaan pengguna selama menggunakan layanan.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <span class="mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mr-3">2.4</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-300 font-light text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">Pain point</span> menunjukkan hambatan atau masalah yang dialami pengguna.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i data-lucide="target" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <span class="mono text-xs text-neutral-600 mr-3">2.5</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-300 font-light text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-white font-medium">Kebutuhan pengguna</span> menjadi dasar perbaikan layanan digital.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SLIDE 5: MIKRO 3 ============ -->
    <div class="slide" data-slide="5">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="fade-in-item mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="tag">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/40"></span>
                    Mikro 3
                </span>
                <span class="slide-counter">06 / 09</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="fade-in-item text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Proposisi Mikro 3</h2>
            <p class="fade-in-item text-neutral-500 text-sm font-light mb-8">Analisis & peluang inovasi</p>
            <div class="fade-in-item glow-line w-32 mb-10"></div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FF4F30]/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-5"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                        <p class="mono text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-3">3.1</p>
                        <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-[0.9rem]">
                            Analisis customer journey membantu <span class="text-white font-medium">menemukan masalah utama</span> pengguna.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FF4F30]/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-5"><i data-lucide="list-ordered" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
                        <p class="mono text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-3">3.2</p>
                        <p class="text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-[0.9rem]">
                            Pain point pengguna dapat digunakan untuk <span class="text-[#FF4F30] font-medium">menentukan prioritas perbaikan</span> layanan.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="fade-in-item proposition-card relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-[#FF4F30]/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-5"><i data-lucide="sparkles" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FF4F30]"></i></div>
